  customer.c_nationkey
from 
  supplier
          inner join region
          on (supplier.s_phone = region.r_name )
        inner join partsupp
        on (partsupp.ps_suppkey < partsupp.ps_suppkey)
      inner join orders
          inner join supplier
            inner join partsupp
              inner join partsupp
                inner join customer
                on (partsupp.ps_partkey = customer.c_custkey )
              on (partsupp.ps_partkey >= partsupp.ps_availqty)
            on (customer.c_mktsegment <= customer.c_phone)
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        inner join customer
            inner join lineitem
              inner join region
              on (lineitem.l_quantity >= lineitem.l_extendedprice)
            on (region.r_name = lineitem.l_shipmode)
          inner join supplier
            inner join nation
            on (nation.n_regionkey > supplier.s_nationkey)
          on (lineitem.l_extendedprice < lineitem.l_tax)
        on (lineitem.l_tax >= orders.o_totalprice)
      on (orders.o_orderdate >= lineitem.l_shipdate)
    inner join region
    on (nation.n_comment is not NULL)

            on (lineitem.l_tax >= lineitem.l_extendedprice)
          inner join lineitem
          on (lineitem.l_receiptdate > lineitem.l_receiptdate)
        on (lineitem.l_discount <= supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join nation
        inner join orders
        on (nation.n_regionkey > nation.n_regionkey)
      on (supplier.s_nationkey >= lineitem.l_partkey)
    on (region.r_comment = region.r_comment )
where lineitem.l_commitdate is NULL;
nl: What are the comments, supply costs, and quantities associated with each part supplier, along with the corresponding supplier and region information, where there is no commit date for the line item?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_tax, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  sum(
    cast(cast(null as money) as money))
from 
  nation
        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_commitdate <= lineitem.l_shipdate)
      inner join part
      on (nation.n_comment = part.p_name )
    inner join partsupp
      inner join part
        inner join orders
        on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
      on (orders.o_orderkey < orders.o_shippriority)
    on (part.p_comment is not NULL)
where part.p_partkey is NULL
limit 95;
nl: What are the tax rates and corresponding part keys for which there are no matching part numbers, considering only those with non-null comments?

sql:
select  
  part.p_retailprice, 
  part.p_name, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as "time") as "time")), 
  part.p_type, 
  part.p_container, 
  part.p_comment, 
  part.p_container
from 
  part
where part.p_size is NULL
limit 158;
nl: What are the retail prices, names, types, containers, and comments of parts that do not have a specified size?

sql:
select  
  min(
    cast(cast(null as anyenum) as anyenum)), 
  supplier.s_address, 
  region.r_comment, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  lineitem.l_shipdate, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  nation.n_comment
from 
  orders
      inner join lineitem
          inner join partsupp
              inner join nation
              on (nation.n_name = nation.n_name)
            inner join lineitem
            on (lineitem.l_tax > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          on (lineitem.l_receiptdate > lineitem.l_commitdate)
        inner join supplier
        on (partsupp.ps_partkey > lineitem.l_partkey)
      on (lineitem.l_shipmode <= lineitem.l_shipinstruct)
    inner join nation
      inner join region
      on (nation.n_regionkey > nation.n_nationkey)
    on (nation.n_regionkey is NULL)
where nation.n_name is not NULL;
nl: What is the minimum value, along with the supplier's address, region comment, supplier key, ship date, region key, and nation comment for each order?

sql:
select distinct 
  supplier.s_name, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  supplier.s_phone, 
  supplier.s_name, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8)), 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as anyenum) as anyenum)), 
  supplier.s_address, 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  supplier.s_address, 
  supplier.s_name, 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  supplier.s_address
from 
  supplier
where supplier.s_nationkey is NULL;
nl: What are the names, supplier keys, phone numbers, and addresses of suppliers that do not have a nation key?

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_comment, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval")), 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  nation.n_nationkey
from 
  supplier
        inner join region
        on (supplier.s_nationkey = region.r_regionkey )
      inner join nation
      on (supplier.s_suppkey >= supplier.s_suppkey)
    inner join nation
          inner join customer
            inner join supplier
            on (customer.c_custkey < supplier.s_suppkey)
          on (supplier.s_acctbal > supplier.s_acctbal)
        inner join customer
        on (supplier.s_phone > customer.c_phone)
      inner join partsupp
          inner join lineitem
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= lineitem.l_tax)
        inner join nation
        on (lineitem.l_extendedprice > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      on (customer.c_mktsegment = lineitem.l_returnflag )
    on (region.r_comment is not NULL)
where lineitem.l_returnflag is NULL
limit 116;
nl: What are the comments, average availability, account balances, available quantities, and nation keys for suppliers who have customers with a specific market segment, along with their corresponding nations and regions?

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  supplier.s_name, 
  lineitem.l_receiptdate
from 
  supplier
    inner join region
      inner join supplier
        inner join lineitem
        on (supplier.s_suppkey = lineitem.l_linenumber)
      on (lineitem.l_discount = lineitem.l_tax)
    on (lineitem.l_shipdate = lineitem.l_receiptdate)
where lineitem.l_commitdate > lineitem.l_receiptdate
limit 147;
nl: What are the names and nationalities of suppliers who have received shipments with a commitment date later than the receipt date, along with the receipt dates?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_shipinstruct, 
  lineitem.l_linenumber, 
  customer.c_acctbal, 
  lineitem.l_orderkey, 
  lineitem.l_extendedprice, 
  lineitem.l_shipinstruct, 
  customer.c_custkey, 
  customer.c_phone, 
  lineitem.l_comment, 
  lineitem.l_receiptdate, 
  customer.c_name
from 
  customer
    inner join lineitem
    on (customer.c_custkey = customer.c_nationkey)
where customer.c_acctbal is NULL;
nl: What are the shipping instructions, line numbers, account balances, order keys, extended prices, customer names, phone numbers, comments, and receipt dates for customers with no account balance?

sql:
select  
  min(
    cast(lineitem.l_discount as "numeric")), 
  orders.o_comment, 
  orders.o_custkey, 
  lineitem.l_discount, 
  lineitem.l_quantity, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as inet) as inet)), 
  lineitem.l_linenumber, 
  lineitem.l_commitdate, 
  lineitem.l_linestatus, 
  lineitem.l_discount, 
  lineitem.l_partkey, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as timetz) as timetz)), 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as int2) as int2)), 
  lineitem.l_returnflag, 
  lineitem.l_receiptdate, 
  orders.o_orderdate, 
  orders.o_orderpriority, 
  lineitem.l_comment
from 
  orders
    inner join lineitem
    on (orders.o_orderstatus is NULL)
where orders.o_totalprice is not NULL
limit 38;
nl: What are the minimum discount rates, customer information, order comments, and other details for a set of 38 orders with non-null total prices?

sql:
select  
  orders.o_orderdate, 
  lineitem.l_suppkey, 
  lineitem.l_suppkey, 
  part.p_size, 
  lineitem.l_returnflag, 
  customer.c_address, 
  part.p_retailprice, 
  part.p_type, 
  part.p_name, 
  orders.o_comment, 
  lineitem.l_partkey
from 
  lineitem
      inner join orders
            inner join part
              inner join lineitem
              on (lineitem.l_returnflag < part.p_brand)
            on (orders.o_clerk = orders.o_orderstatus)
          inner join lineitem
          on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct <= lineitem.l_shipmode)
        inner join customer
              inner join part
              on (customer.c_mktsegment > customer.c_mktsegment)
            inner join nation
            on (customer.c_comment = nation.n_comment )
          inner join part
                inner join supplier
                on (part.p_retailprice = supplier.s_acctbal)
              inner join orders
              on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
            inner join customer
            on (orders.o_orderdate >= orders.o_orderdate)
          on (nation.n_nationkey <= part.p_size)
        on (lineitem.l_commitdate < orders.o_orderdate)
      on (orders.o_orderdate = lineitem.l_commitdate)
    inner join part
      inner join orders
      on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
    on (part.p_name is not NULL)
where lineitem.l_returnflag is NULL
limit 116;
nl: What are the order dates, supplier keys, part sizes, return flags, customer addresses, retail prices, part types, part names, order comments, and part keys for orders with no return flag?

sql:
select  
  customer.c_acctbal, 
  customer.c_comment,

    cast(cast(null as "timestamp") as "timestamp")),

    cast(cast(null as "time") as "time")),

from 
  customer
where customer.c_phone is not NULL;

sql:

where customer.c_nationkey is not NULL

sql:
select  
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8)),

  orders.o_shippriority
from 
  partsupp
    inner join nation
      inner join part
        inner join orders
          inner join region
            inner join nation
            on (nation.n_nationkey < nation.n_regionkey)
          on (orders.o_totalprice >= orders.o_totalprice)
        on (part.p_mfgr >= nation.n_name)
      on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
    on (region.r_comment is NULL)
where part.p_brand is NULL;

where partsupp.ps_partkey is NULL;

sql:
select  
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  nation.n_nationkey
from 
  region
    inner join supplier
          inner join nation
              inner join partsupp
              on (nation.n_name > nation.n_name)
            inner join region
            on (partsupp.ps_availqty > partsupp.ps_partkey)
          on (supplier.s_acctbal <= supplier.s_acctbal)
        inner join partsupp
        on (supplier.s_name >= region.r_name)
      inner join supplier
        inner join supplier
        on (supplier.s_nationkey < supplier.s_suppkey)
      on (supplier.s_phone < supplier.s_name)
    on (partsupp.ps_comment is NULL)
where supplier.s_acctbal is not NULL

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_comment, 
  customer.c_name
from 
  supplier
      inner join region
            inner join partsupp
            on (region.r_comment = partsupp.ps_comment )
          inner join customer
          on (region.r_name = customer.c_phone )
        inner join customer
        on (region.r_name < customer.c_mktsegment)
      on (supplier.s_nationkey < partsupp.ps_partkey)
    inner join customer
    on (partsupp.ps_suppkey is NULL)
where customer.c_custkey is NULL
limit 38;
nl: What are the comments from suppliers and names of customers where the supplier's nation key is less than the part supply's part key, and the customer's market segment is greater than or equal to the region name, but the customer's key is missing?

sql:
select  
  orders.o_clerk, 
  region.r_name
from 
  nation
          inner join part
          on (part.p_size > nation.n_regionkey)
        inner join orders
        on (part.p_brand = orders.o_orderstatus )
      inner join region
      on (part.p_mfgr = region.r_name )
    inner join partsupp
      inner join partsupp
            inner join region
              inner join region
              on (region.r_name > region.r_name)
            on (partsupp.ps_suppkey <= partsupp.ps_partkey)
          inner join part
          on (region.r_regionkey < region.r_regionkey)
        inner join region
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      on (part.p_container <= region.r_name)
    on (part.p_type is not NULL)
where part.p_retailprice < partsupp.ps_supplycost;
nl: What are the names of clerks and regions associated with orders where the retail price of a part is less than its supply cost?

sql:
select  
  customer.c_custkey
from 
  lineitem
        inner join region
          inner join partsupp
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        on (lineitem.l_receiptdate > lineitem.l_receiptdate)
      inner join customer
        inner join customer
        on (customer.c_acctbal > customer.c_acctbal)
      on (customer.c_mktsegment > region.r_name)
    inner join part
      inner join nation
      on (part.p_comment = nation.n_comment )
    on (customer.c_phone is NULL)
where partsupp.ps_partkey is not NULL
limit 105;
nl: What customer account keys have a higher account balance and are in a market segment that matches a region name, with a null phone number, and are related to a part with a matching comment to a nation's comment?

sql:
select  
  customer.c_name, 
  lineitem.l_receiptdate
from 
  lineitem
      inner join supplier
        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_linenumber < lineitem.l_suppkey)
      on (lineitem.l_returnflag <= lineitem.l_shipmode)
    inner join customer
      inner join part
        inner join lineitem
        on (part.p_container = lineitem.l_returnflag )
      on (lineitem.l_receiptdate > lineitem.l_receiptdate)
    on (lineitem.l_comment = part.p_name )
where lineitem.l_extendedprice is not NULL;
nl: What are the names of customers and their corresponding receipt dates for orders with a non-null extended price?

sql:
select  
  customer.c_phone, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  customer.c_mktsegment, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_name, 
  region.r_name
from 
  customer
          inner join nation
          on (customer.c_acctbal = customer.c_acctbal)
        inner join region
        on (customer.c_custkey >= customer.c_nationkey)
      inner join nation
      on (customer.c_acctbal = customer.c_acctbal)
    inner join part
    on (customer.c_mktsegment is not NULL)
where nation.n_regionkey > nation.n_nationkey
limit 83;
nl: What are the phone numbers, market segments, and corresponding nation and region details for a specific set of customers?

sql:

  supplier.s_name
from 
  nation
      inner join customer
      on (customer.c_custkey >= customer.c_custkey)
    inner join supplier
      inner join supplier
      on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
    on (customer.c_name is not NULL)
where supplier.s_suppkey is not NULL;

sql:

from

sql:

  partsupp.ps_supplycost
from

    inner join supplier
        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_orderkey <= supplier.s_nationkey)
      inner join region
      on (lineitem.l_commitdate > lineitem.l_receiptdate)
    on (lineitem.l_suppkey is NULL)
where supplier.s_acctbal is not NULL;

sql:

  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_comment,

    cast(lineitem.l_commitdate as date)), 
  region.r_name
from

        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_shipmode < lineitem.l_returnflag)
      inner join region
      on (lineitem.l_commitdate > lineitem.l_shipdate)

    on (partsupp.ps_availqty is NULL)
where lineitem.l_comment is not NULL;
nl: What are the regions, supplier phone numbers, part keys, and comments for which there is a non-null comment in the line item, along with the maximum commit date and an empty availability quantity?

sql:

  lineitem.l_orderkey
from 
  lineitem
where lineitem.l_returnflag is NULL;
nl: What are the commit dates, part keys, ship modes, and order keys for all line items that do not have a return flag?

sql:
select  
  customer.c_name, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as anyenum) as anyenum)), 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as int2) as int2)), 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as anyarray) as anyarray)), 
  customer.c_phone, 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as anyarray) as anyarray)), 
  min(
    cast(customer.c_mktsegment as bpchar)), 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as oid) as oid)),

  avg(

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_returnflag, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as xid8) as xid8)), 
  lineitem.l_orderkey, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey
from 
  customer
        inner join lineitem
          inner join nation
            inner join partsupp
            on (nation.n_regionkey = partsupp.ps_partkey )
          on (lineitem.l_linestatus >= lineitem.l_shipmode)
        on (lineitem.l_partkey <= partsupp.ps_suppkey)
      inner join region
          inner join nation
          on (region.r_regionkey = nation.n_nationkey )
        inner join lineitem
            inner join part
            on (lineitem.l_partkey = part.p_partkey )
          inner join nation
          on (lineitem.l_discount <= lineitem.l_extendedprice)
        on (nation.n_name = lineitem.l_shipinstruct)
      on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct < nation.n_name)
    inner join customer
    on (customer.c_nationkey is NULL)
where partsupp.ps_supplycost < lineitem.l_extendedprice
limit 69;
nl: What are the return flags, order keys, and supplier keys for the top 69 products with a supply cost lower than their extended price?

sql:

  supplier.s_address,

sql:
select  
  nation.n_comment,

  nation.n_regionkey,

limit 24;
nl: What are the comments, nation keys, and region keys for up to 24 nations that have a comment?

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_address, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as inet) as inet)), 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  supplier.s_address, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8)), 
  supplier.s_name
from 
  supplier
where supplier.s_acctbal > supplier.s_acctbal;
nl: What is the address, minimum and average balance, and comment for each supplier with an account balance greater than itself?

sql:
select  
  part.p_container, 
  part.p_container, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8)), 
  part.p_size, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  max(
    cast(lineitem.l_receiptdate as date))
from 
  part
            inner join customer
            on (part.p_comment = customer.c_name )
          inner join part
            inner join lineitem
            on (part.p_comment = lineitem.l_comment )
          on (customer.c_address = part.p_name )
        inner join supplier
        on (customer.c_address = supplier.s_address )
      inner join supplier
        inner join part
        on (supplier.s_acctbal > supplier.s_acctbal)
      on (supplier.s_phone >= part.p_mfgr)
    inner join part
          inner join part
              inner join customer
              on (customer.c_custkey <= part.p_partkey)
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_orderpriority > customer.c_phone)
          on (customer.c_acctbal > orders.o_totalprice)
        inner join part
            inner join part
                inner join part
                on (part.p_brand > part.p_mfgr)
              inner join region
              on (part.p_brand = part.p_brand)
            on (part.p_partkey <= part.p_partkey)
          inner join region
          on (part.p_brand >= part.p_brand)
        on (region.r_regionkey < orders.o_custkey)
      inner join part
        inner join nation
        on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
      on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
    on (part.p_name = customer.c_name )
where part.p_type is NULL;

sql:

sql:

  part.p_type,

sql:

sql:

    inner join region
    on (partsupp.ps_partkey is not NULL)
where partsupp.ps_availqty is NULL;
nl: What regions have no available quantity of parts?

sql:
select  
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  nation.n_name, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as inet) as inet)), 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_name
from 
  nation
where nation.n_name = nation.n_name
limit 166;
nl: What are the names and region keys of 166 nations?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_discount, 
  part.p_type, 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  part.p_name, 
  part.p_size, 
  orders.o_totalprice, 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  lineitem.l_suppkey
from 
  part
    inner join orders
        inner join partsupp
            inner join lineitem
              inner join customer
                inner join part
                on (part.p_container < customer.c_mktsegment)
              on (lineitem.l_discount = part.p_retailprice )
            on (lineitem.l_discount > lineitem.l_extendedprice)
          inner join orders
          on (customer.c_mktsegment < lineitem.l_returnflag)
        on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
      inner join supplier
      on (lineitem.l_discount < lineitem.l_extendedprice)
    on (part.p_retailprice = orders.o_totalprice )
where partsupp.ps_suppkey is NULL
limit 56;
nl: What are the discount rates, product types, account balances, comments, and names of products that have a certain size, along with their total order prices and supplier comments, where there is no supplier key?

sql:
select  
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_nationkey,

        inner join nation

where partsupp.ps_partkey is not NULL

    on (partsupp.ps_supplycost > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
where partsupp.ps_supplycost is not NULL
limit 124;

sql:
select  
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_comment
from 
  region
        inner join region
        on (region.r_name = region.r_name )
      inner join partsupp
        inner join nation
                inner join region
                on (nation.n_name > nation.n_name)
              inner join supplier
              on (nation.n_name = supplier.s_name )
            inner join supplier
            on (nation.n_regionkey < nation.n_nationkey)
          inner join part
              inner join part
              on (part.p_partkey = part.p_partkey)
            inner join supplier
            on (part.p_retailprice <= supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (supplier.s_acctbal >= supplier.s_acctbal)
        on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = nation.n_nationkey )
      on (part.p_retailprice < supplier.s_acctbal)
    inner join region
      inner join nation
      on (nation.n_name >= nation.n_name)
    on (part.p_container < supplier.s_name)
where supplier.s_nationkey is NULL;
nl: What suppliers do not have a corresponding nation, considering the relationships between parts, suppliers, and nations?

sql:
select  
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  orders.o_orderkey, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as xid8) as xid8)), 
  supplier.s_address
from 
  supplier
    inner join lineitem
            inner join nation
            on (lineitem.l_comment = nation.n_comment )
          inner join part
          on (lineitem.l_receiptdate < lineitem.l_commitdate)
        inner join orders
        on (lineitem.l_linestatus = orders.o_orderstatus)
      inner join partsupp
      on (orders.o_shippriority = partsupp.ps_partkey )
    on (supplier.s_name > part.p_mfgr)
where part.p_mfgr is NULL
limit 134;

limit 99;
nl: What are the comments and keys for nations that do not have a name?

sql:
select  
  customer.c_mktsegment, 
  lineitem.l_comment, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  region.r_comment, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "timestamp") as "timestamp")), 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  part.p_brand, 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  customer.c_name
from 
  customer
        inner join customer
        on (customer.c_phone <= customer.c_mktsegment)
      inner join part
          inner join part
            inner join lineitem
            on (part.p_container >= part.p_brand)
          on (lineitem.l_tax >= lineitem.l_tax)
        inner join orders
          inner join region
          on (region.r_regionkey = orders.o_custkey)
        on (part.p_comment = region.r_comment )
      on (customer.c_mktsegment = lineitem.l_linestatus)
    inner join nation
        inner join customer
          inner join supplier
          on (customer.c_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
        on (supplier.s_phone < customer.c_phone)
      inner join part
          inner join part
          on (part.p_partkey = part.p_partkey)
        inner join region
        on (part.p_brand = part.p_brand)
      on (customer.c_custkey = part.p_size)
    on (orders.o_orderdate >= lineitem.l_receiptdate)
where part.p_name is NULL;
nl: What customers, with their market segment, name, and nation, have a specific brand of parts from suppliers with certain comments, in regions with particular comments, where the order date is later than or equal to the receipt date, and there is no part name?

sql:
select  
  region.r_name,

  region.r_name, 
  region.r_name
from 
  region
where region.r_comment is not NULL

sql:
select  
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as anyenum) as anyenum)), 
  partsupp.ps_comment, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8))
from 
  partsupp
where partsupp.ps_suppkey is NULL
limit 91;
nl: What are the comments, part keys, and supply costs for the first 91 parts with no supplier key?

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  region.r_comment, 
  region.r_comment, 
  sum(
    cast(supplier.s_suppkey as int4)), 
  supplier.s_address, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  region.r_name
from 
  supplier
      inner join part
        inner join orders
          inner join nation
          on (orders.o_totalprice >= orders.o_totalprice)
        on (orders.o_totalprice > orders.o_totalprice)
      on (supplier.s_acctbal = orders.o_totalprice )
    inner join region
        inner join supplier
            inner join nation
            on (supplier.s_acctbal < supplier.s_acctbal)
          inner join region
          on (supplier.s_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey)
        on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join supplier
      on (region.r_regionkey <= supplier.s_nationkey)
    on (orders.o_orderkey = region.r_regionkey )
where nation.n_nationkey is not NULL;
nl: What are the supplier keys, region comments, and addresses, along with the sum of their keys, for each region, where the nation key is not null?

sql:
select  
  orders.o_totalprice, 
  nation.n_name
from 
  supplier
            inner join lineitem
            on (supplier.s_phone = lineitem.l_returnflag )
          inner join part
              inner join orders
                inner join partsupp
                on (orders.o_comment = partsupp.ps_comment )
              on (orders.o_orderkey <= orders.o_shippriority)
            inner join orders
                inner join orders
                on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
              inner join customer
              on (orders.o_custkey >= customer.c_custkey)
            on (orders.o_shippriority < orders.o_shippriority)
          on (lineitem.l_commitdate < orders.o_orderdate)
        inner join partsupp
          inner join part
            inner join nation
            on (part.p_size < nation.n_nationkey)
          on (nation.n_nationkey <= part.p_size)
        on (orders.o_shippriority > customer.c_custkey)
      inner join region
      on (nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey )
    inner join nation
    on (partsupp.ps_partkey <= orders.o_custkey)
where orders.o_orderpriority >= orders.o_orderstatus
limit 142;
nl: What are the total prices of orders and their corresponding nation names where the order priority is higher than or equal to the order status?

sql:
select  
  region.r_regionkey, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as float4) as float4)), 
  part.p_container, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as int2) as int2)), 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval")), 
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  part.p_partkey, 
  region.r_name, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost
from 
  partsupp
      inner join region
      on (region.r_regionkey <= partsupp.ps_partkey)
    inner join part
    on (region.r_regionkey is not NULL)
where part.p_retailprice = partsupp.ps_supplycost
limit 98;
nl: What are the regions, corresponding part keys, available quantities, and supply costs for which the retail price matches the supply cost, along with the container type and region names?

sql:
select  
  nation.n_comment, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as timetz) as timetz)), 
  customer.c_address
from 
  nation
              inner join region
              on (nation.n_regionkey > region.r_regionkey)
            inner join nation
            on (nation.n_name >= nation.n_name)
          inner join part
            inner join lineitem
            on (part.p_container > lineitem.l_linestatus)
          on (region.r_comment = lineitem.l_comment )
        inner join partsupp
          inner join nation
          on (partsupp.ps_partkey <= nation.n_nationkey)
        on (lineitem.l_quantity < lineitem.l_discount)
      inner join customer
      on (nation.n_name < nation.n_name)
    inner join lineitem
    on (partsupp.ps_availqty = lineitem.l_orderkey )
where nation.n_comment is not NULL;
nl: What are the comments, maximum time, and addresses of customers associated with nations that have a comment?

sql:
select  
  part.p_mfgr,

  part.p_type, 
  part.p_brand,

  part.p_mfgr, 
  region.r_regionkey
from 
  region
    inner join part
    on (part.p_retailprice is NULL)
where part.p_name is not NULL
limit 183;
nl: What are the names and details of parts from various manufacturers in different regions where retail prices are not available?

sql:
select

    cast(cast(null as bpchar) as bpchar)),

from

where partsupp.ps_supplycost is not NULL;

sql:
select  
  customer.c_comment,

    cast(cast(null as anyenum) as anyenum)),

    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval")),

sql:

    cast(cast(null as xid8) as xid8)),

  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_comment,

  nation.n_regionkey, 
  nation.n_regionkey,

    inner join nation
      inner join region
      on (region.r_name > nation.n_name)

limit 190;

sql:
select  
  nation.n_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  nation.n_name, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  orders.o_orderkey, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as anyenum) as anyenum)), 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  orders.o_orderkey, 
  orders.o_orderkey, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  orders.o_comment, 
  sum(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8)), 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as text) as text))
from 
  orders
    inner join partsupp
      inner join nation
      on (nation.n_regionkey < partsupp.ps_availqty)
    on (orders.o_totalprice is NULL)
where nation.n_regionkey is not NULL
limit 30;
nl: What are the names, comments, and regions of nations, along with their corresponding supply costs, order keys, order statuses, and comments, for a limited selection of 30 cases?

sql:
select  
  part.p_mfgr, 
  part.p_brand
from 
  part
where part.p_retailprice is not NULL
limit 136;
nl: What are the manufacturers and brands of parts that have a retail price?

sql:
select  
  max(
    cast(lineitem.l_shipdate as date))
from 
  orders
      inner join lineitem
        inner join part
            inner join nation
            on (part.p_retailprice <= part.p_retailprice)
          inner join region
          on (nation.n_regionkey = region.r_regionkey )
        on (lineitem.l_tax = lineitem.l_discount)
      on (orders.o_custkey > orders.o_shippriority)
    inner join nation
        inner join partsupp
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      inner join supplier
      on (supplier.s_phone = supplier.s_phone)
    on (supplier.s_comment is not NULL)
where supplier.s_nationkey is NULL;
nl: What is the latest shipping date for orders where the supplier's nation key is unknown?

sql:
select  
  sum(
    cast(cast(null as "interval") as "interval"))
from 
  region
      inner join part
        inner join nation
          inner join partsupp
            inner join supplier
              inner join customer
              on (supplier.s_phone >= supplier.s_name)
            on (supplier.s_nationkey >= customer.c_custkey)
          on (customer.c_acctbal >= customer.c_acctbal)
        on (customer.c_phone > supplier.s_phone)
      on (supplier.s_suppkey >= supplier.s_suppkey)
    inner join supplier
    on (nation.n_regionkey is not NULL)
where customer.c_nationkey is not NULL;
nl: What is the total duration of all relationships between customers and suppliers across different regions?

sql:
select  
  part.p_container, 
  part.p_name, 
  supplier.s_address, 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  region.r_comment, 
  supplier.s_address
from 
  supplier
        inner join nation
        on (nation.n_name >= supplier.s_name)
      inner join region
      on (supplier.s_name <= supplier.s_name)
    inner join part
      inner join supplier
        inner join region
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_totalprice > orders.o_totalprice)
          inner join supplier
            inner join lineitem
              inner join orders
              on (lineitem.l_shipdate > lineitem.l_receiptdate)
            on (orders.o_shippriority <= orders.o_shippriority)
          on (orders.o_clerk = supplier.s_name )
        on (lineitem.l_discount > orders.o_totalprice)
      on (part.p_partkey < orders.o_custkey)
    on (supplier.s_name is not NULL)
where orders.o_custkey is not NULL;

        on (orders.o_custkey = nation.n_nationkey )

select

    cast(cast(null as pg_lsn) as pg_lsn)),

    cast(lineitem.l_discount as "numeric")), 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  orders.o_orderkey, 
  region.r_name, 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as anyenum) as anyenum)), 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  region.r_comment
from 
  supplier
    inner join nation
              inner join region
              on (nation.n_regionkey < region.r_regionkey)
            inner join customer
              inner join orders
                inner join region
                on (orders.o_shippriority <= orders.o_orderkey)
              on (orders.o_orderstatus < customer.c_mktsegment)
            on (orders.o_orderkey <= customer.c_nationkey)
          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_totalprice >= orders.o_totalprice)
        inner join lineitem
            inner join customer
            on (lineitem.l_returnflag <= lineitem.l_linestatus)
          inner join region
            inner join region
            on (region.r_regionkey < region.r_regionkey)
          on (lineitem.l_commitdate < lineitem.l_receiptdate)
        on (orders.o_orderdate >= lineitem.l_commitdate)
      inner join part
      on (lineitem.l_extendedprice <= orders.o_totalprice)
    on (supplier.s_name = part.p_mfgr )
where lineitem.l_extendedprice >= customer.c_acctbal
limit 156;

from

              inner join part

            on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
          inner join lineitem
          on (region.r_comment = lineitem.l_comment )
        on (customer.c_mktsegment = part.p_mfgr )
      inner join nation
          inner join lineitem
              inner join region
              on (lineitem.l_discount < lineitem.l_discount)
            inner join part
            on (lineitem.l_discount <= lineitem.l_quantity)
          on (lineitem.l_quantity >= lineitem.l_discount)
        inner join part
            inner join nation
              inner join lineitem
              on (nation.n_regionkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )
            on (part.p_retailprice < part.p_retailprice)
          inner join region
          on (lineitem.l_tax >= lineitem.l_tax)
        on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct = nation.n_name)
      on (region.r_regionkey < region.r_regionkey)
    inner join nation
        inner join part
        on (nation.n_name >= part.p_container)
      inner join region
      on (part.p_partkey = part.p_partkey)
    on (region.r_name = region.r_name )
where part.p_name is not NULL

          inner join orders
            inner join nation
              inner join part
              on (nation.n_nationkey < part.p_size)
            on (part.p_retailprice = orders.o_totalprice)
          on (orders.o_orderstatus >= part.p_mfgr)
        on (lineitem.l_partkey = customer.c_custkey )
      inner join lineitem
      on (lineitem.l_partkey = nation.n_regionkey)
    on (orders.o_orderpriority is NULL)
where lineitem.l_linenumber < lineitem.l_suppkey

          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)

    cast(cast(null as timetz) as timetz)),

  nation.n_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  customer.c_address
from 
  nation
          inner join part
            inner join region
              inner join customer
              on (region.r_regionkey <= region.r_regionkey)
            on (part.p_type = region.r_comment )
          on (part.p_retailprice = customer.c_acctbal)
        inner join supplier
            inner join nation
            on (nation.n_name < supplier.s_phone)
          inner join region
          on (supplier.s_name >= supplier.s_name)
        on (part.p_retailprice = supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join customer
      on (part.p_size = customer.c_custkey )
    inner join nation
          inner join part
                inner join orders
                on (part.p_retailprice >= part.p_retailprice)
              inner join customer
                inner join nation
                  inner join partsupp
                  on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
                on (nation.n_nationkey <= customer.c_nationkey)
              on (partsupp.ps_suppkey <= orders.o_custkey)
            inner join part
            on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
          on (partsupp.ps_partkey = partsupp.ps_suppkey)
        inner join customer
        on (customer.c_address = customer.c_name )
      inner join part
      on (orders.o_orderpriority > nation.n_name)
    on (part.p_size is not NULL)
where nation.n_name >= customer.c_mktsegment

                inner join orders
                on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
              on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
            on (supplier.s_nationkey = part.p_partkey)
          inner join part
          on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
        inner join region
        on (supplier.s_name = region.r_name )
      inner join nation
          inner join lineitem
          on (nation.n_regionkey <= nation.n_regionkey)
        inner join supplier
          inner join region
            inner join partsupp
              inner join supplier
              on (supplier.s_nationkey >= partsupp.ps_partkey)
            on (supplier.s_name >= region.r_name)
          on (region.r_name < supplier.s_phone)
        on (supplier.s_suppkey > lineitem.l_orderkey)
      on (orders.o_clerk = nation.n_name )
    inner join lineitem

from

            inner join partsupp
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          inner join nation
            inner join partsupp
              inner join partsupp
              on (partsupp.ps_partkey = partsupp.ps_availqty)
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          on (nation.n_name <= nation.n_name)
        inner join supplier
        on (supplier.s_suppkey <= partsupp.ps_availqty)
      inner join orders
      on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = orders.o_orderkey )
    inner join nation
        inner join part
        on (part.p_size <= part.p_size)
      inner join supplier
        inner join part
        on (part.p_brand = part.p_brand)
      on (part.p_partkey <= part.p_size)
    on (orders.o_orderpriority <= supplier.s_phone)
where partsupp.ps_availqty <= partsupp.ps_availqty;

select  
  nation.n_name,

  lineitem.l_shipdate, 
  lineitem.l_suppkey,

  supplier.s_nationkey
from 
  nation
        inner join lineitem
            inner join part
            on (part.p_retailprice >= lineitem.l_tax)
          inner join nation
                inner join lineitem
                on (lineitem.l_shipdate < lineitem.l_commitdate)
              inner join customer
              on (lineitem.l_orderkey <= customer.c_nationkey)
            inner join nation
            on (customer.c_nationkey < nation.n_regionkey)
          on (customer.c_mktsegment > lineitem.l_returnflag)
        on (part.p_container > customer.c_mktsegment)
      inner join part
        inner join nation
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_phone < supplier.s_name)
          inner join nation
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_name >= supplier.s_name)
          on (supplier.s_suppkey = nation.n_nationkey )
        on (nation.n_name < part.p_mfgr)
      on (nation.n_comment = nation.n_comment )
    inner join lineitem
      inner join part
      on (lineitem.l_commitdate < lineitem.l_shipdate)
    on (lineitem.l_quantity = lineitem.l_tax)
where lineitem.l_discount <= part.p_retailprice

from

      inner join supplier
            inner join supplier
              inner join orders
              on (orders.o_totalprice = orders.o_totalprice)
            on (supplier.s_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey)
          inner join customer
            inner join region
              inner join supplier
                  inner join orders
                  on (supplier.s_acctbal > supplier.s_acctbal)
                inner join nation
                on (nation.n_name > orders.o_orderpriority)
              on (orders.o_totalprice <= orders.o_totalprice)
            on (orders.o_clerk > region.r_name)
          on (supplier.s_name = orders.o_orderstatus )
        inner join partsupp
          inner join orders
          on (partsupp.ps_partkey < orders.o_orderkey)
        on (region.r_regionkey = orders.o_orderkey )
      on (partsupp.ps_supplycost <= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
    inner join orders
        inner join supplier
          inner join region
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_acctbal < supplier.s_acctbal)

        on (orders.o_totalprice >= supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join part

        inner join nation

select  
  orders.o_orderdate, 
  orders.o_totalprice, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  region.r_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  sum(
    cast(cast(null as float4) as float4)), 
  lineitem.l_returnflag, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as timetz) as timetz)), 
  customer.c_name, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  orders.o_comment, 
  customer.c_custkey, 
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  orders.o_clerk, 
  orders.o_orderpriority, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  customer.c_mktsegment, 
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  customer.c_mktsegment, 
  customer.c_mktsegment
from 
  orders
      inner join partsupp
        inner join partsupp
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_clerk <= orders.o_orderstatus)
          inner join region
          on (partsupp.ps_partkey >= orders.o_shippriority)
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      on (orders.o_orderpriority < region.r_name)
    inner join customer
      inner join lineitem
      on (lineitem.l_tax <= customer.c_acctbal)
    on (orders.o_custkey is NULL)
where partsupp.ps_comment is NULL;
nl: What are the order dates, total prices, supplier keys, region comments, part keys, return flags, supply costs, customer names, customer market segments, and order statuses for orders with no supplier comment?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_suppkey, 
  orders.o_custkey, 
  lineitem.l_comment, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as anyenum) as anyenum)), 
  orders.o_orderkey
from 
  partsupp
      inner join customer
      on (partsupp.ps_partkey >= partsupp.ps_availqty)
    inner join orders
        inner join lineitem
        on (orders.o_orderdate = lineitem.l_commitdate)
      inner join orders
      on (orders.o_orderstatus > lineitem.l_returnflag)
    on (orders.o_clerk is not NULL)
where partsupp.ps_supplycost >= lineitem.l_quantity;
nl: What are the supplier keys, customer keys, and order comments for orders with a certain status, where the supply cost meets or exceeds the ordered quantity?

sql:

limit 169;
nl: What brands of parts are also used as containers?

sql:
select  
  region.r_name, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  supplier.s_phone
from 
  nation
      inner join customer
          inner join region
          on (customer.c_acctbal <= customer.c_acctbal)
        inner join supplier
        on (region.r_comment = supplier.s_address )
      on (supplier.s_phone <= supplier.s_phone)
    inner join region
        inner join lineitem
            inner join supplier
              inner join customer
              on (customer.c_custkey <= customer.c_nationkey)
            on (lineitem.l_extendedprice = supplier.s_acctbal )
          inner join orders
              inner join nation
                  inner join customer
                  on (customer.c_phone > customer.c_phone)
                inner join region
                on (region.r_name = customer.c_mktsegment)
              on (orders.o_orderstatus = nation.n_name )
            inner join supplier
            on (nation.n_name > nation.n_name)
          on (lineitem.l_commitdate < orders.o_orderdate)
        on (region.r_name = lineitem.l_returnflag )
      inner join part
        inner join customer
        on (part.p_retailprice < customer.c_acctbal)
      on (customer.c_custkey <= orders.o_shippriority)
    on (customer.c_custkey is NULL)
where part.p_brand is NULL
limit 153;
nl: What regions, nations, and suppliers have customers with no account balance, along with the supplier's phone number?

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_quantity, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8)), 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as oid) as oid)), 
  lineitem.l_commitdate, 
  supplier.s_phone, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as timestamptz) as timestamptz)), 
  customer.c_phone, 
  lineitem.l_comment, 
  customer.c_nationkey
from 
  nation
          inner join supplier
          on (nation.n_nationkey < supplier.s_suppkey)
        inner join nation
          inner join customer
          on (customer.c_acctbal > customer.c_acctbal)
        on (nation.n_name = nation.n_name )
      inner join customer
      on (supplier.s_acctbal <= supplier.s_acctbal)
    inner join lineitem
    on (nation.n_name = lineitem.l_returnflag )
where lineitem.l_shipdate >= lineitem.l_receiptdate
limit 65;
nl: What are the quantities, regions, commitment dates, phone numbers, and comments for a specific set of customers and suppliers with certain account balances and shipment details?

  supplier.s_acctbal,

  supplier.s_comment, 
  supplier.s_name
from 
  supplier
      inner join lineitem
      on (lineitem.l_linenumber < lineitem.l_orderkey)
    inner join region
      inner join supplier
      on (region.r_name = region.r_name)
    on (lineitem.l_suppkey = supplier.s_suppkey )
where region.r_comment is NULL
limit 113;
nl: What are the names, account balances, addresses, and comments of suppliers from regions with no comment, along with their corresponding nation keys?

sql:
select  
  max(
    cast(cast(null as oid) as oid)), 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as text) as text))
from 
  customer
        inner join part
          inner join supplier
          on (part.p_size <= part.p_partkey)
        on (part.p_container > customer.c_phone)
      inner join part
        inner join customer
        on (part.p_brand > part.p_brand)
      on (customer.c_mktsegment >= customer.c_mktsegment)
    inner join region
      inner join orders
      on (orders.o_clerk > orders.o_orderpriority)
    on (part.p_mfgr is not NULL)
where customer.c_phone <= part.p_mfgr;
nl: What is the maximum and minimum value of certain attributes for customers with a phone number less than or equal to the manufacturer of their parts, across different regions?

  orders.o_clerk,

  lineitem.l_orderkey,

    cast(cast(null as timestamptz) as timestamptz)), 
  orders.o_totalprice, 
  lineitem.l_commitdate,

sql:
select

  supplier.s_address,

  region.r_comment,

    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8))
from

          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        inner join supplier
        on (partsupp.ps_availqty <= supplier.s_nationkey)

    on (supplier.s_phone is NULL)

sql:
select  
  nation.n_name, 
  nation.n_name, 
  customer.c_address, 
  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty
from 
  nation
        inner join nation
        on (nation.n_comment = nation.n_comment )
      inner join supplier
      on (supplier.s_suppkey <= nation.n_regionkey)
    inner join customer
        inner join partsupp
            inner join partsupp
            on (partsupp.ps_suppkey <= partsupp.ps_suppkey)
          inner join partsupp
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        on (customer.c_nationkey = partsupp.ps_partkey )
      inner join nation
        inner join nation
        on (nation.n_nationkey <= nation.n_nationkey)
      on (nation.n_name >= customer.c_phone)
    on (nation.n_nationkey is not NULL)
where nation.n_nationkey is not NULL

  customer.c_acctbal,

from

    inner join nation
        inner join orders
        on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
      inner join nation
        inner join region
          inner join partsupp
          on (region.r_comment = partsupp.ps_comment )
        on (region.r_name = region.r_name)

sql:
select

  part.p_partkey,

  nation.n_comment, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  part.p_comment
from 
  part
        inner join part
          inner join nation
            inner join partsupp
            on (nation.n_name = nation.n_name)
          on (part.p_mfgr > part.p_container)
        on (part.p_retailprice >= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      inner join nation
      on (part.p_brand = part.p_container)
    inner join part
        inner join customer
        on (customer.c_nationkey > part.p_partkey)
      inner join region
      on (part.p_brand = part.p_mfgr)
    on (nation.n_regionkey = customer.c_custkey )
where customer.c_name is not NULL;

  customer.c_acctbal
from

        inner join customer

          inner join orders
          on (part.p_partkey = orders.o_orderkey )

        on (supplier.s_phone > nation.n_name)

        on (customer.c_nationkey = customer.c_custkey)

  partsupp.ps_supplycost
from 
  customer
      inner join supplier
        inner join customer
            inner join region
            on (customer.c_acctbal <= customer.c_acctbal)
          inner join nation
              inner join partsupp
              on (nation.n_regionkey > partsupp.ps_partkey)
            inner join region
              inner join orders
              on (orders.o_orderstatus >= region.r_name)
            on (orders.o_totalprice >= orders.o_totalprice)
          on (orders.o_totalprice < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        on (customer.c_custkey < region.r_regionkey)
      on (nation.n_regionkey <= customer.c_nationkey)
    inner join region
          inner join nation
            inner join customer
            on (nation.n_regionkey <= nation.n_regionkey)
          on (nation.n_name > customer.c_phone)
        inner join orders
          inner join partsupp
            inner join region
            on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = region.r_regionkey )
          on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
        on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
      inner join lineitem
      on (partsupp.ps_partkey = nation.n_nationkey)
    on (region.r_comment is NULL)

  count(*), 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as oid) as oid)), 
  customer.c_nationkey
from 
  orders
          inner join part
            inner join lineitem
            on (lineitem.l_tax < lineitem.l_tax)
          on (orders.o_clerk = lineitem.l_returnflag )
        inner join orders
        on (orders.o_totalprice > orders.o_totalprice)
      inner join region
          inner join nation
          on (region.r_regionkey > nation.n_nationkey)
        inner join part
        on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
      on (part.p_retailprice = orders.o_totalprice)
    inner join partsupp
      inner join region
              inner join lineitem
              on (lineitem.l_quantity >= lineitem.l_extendedprice)
            inner join customer
            on (customer.c_nationkey >= lineitem.l_linenumber)
          inner join partsupp
            inner join partsupp
              inner join lineitem
              on (lineitem.l_shipdate >= lineitem.l_commitdate)
            on (lineitem.l_extendedprice = lineitem.l_discount)
          on (lineitem.l_suppkey < partsupp.ps_suppkey)
        inner join nation
        on (nation.n_nationkey >= lineitem.l_orderkey)
      on (lineitem.l_tax > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
    on (lineitem.l_linestatus >= lineitem.l_returnflag)

    cast(cast(null as timetz) as timetz))
from 
  customer
    inner join lineitem
          inner join partsupp
            inner join customer
            on (customer.c_phone = customer.c_mktsegment)
          on (lineitem.l_extendedprice = partsupp.ps_supplycost )
        inner join region
        on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct > lineitem.l_linestatus)
      inner join nation
      on (lineitem.l_linenumber = partsupp.ps_partkey)
    on (region.r_regionkey >= customer.c_nationkey)
where customer.c_address is not NULL;

sql:
select distinct 
  nation.n_regionkey, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  customer.c_acctbal, 
  region.r_name, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  region.r_name, 
  region.r_comment, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  customer.c_mktsegment, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as float8) as float8)), 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  customer.c_phone, 
  nation.n_name, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as text) as text)), 
  nation.n_name, 
  orders.o_clerk, 
  nation.n_name, 
  nation.n_comment, 
  avg(
    cast(customer.c_acctbal as "numeric"))
from 
  nation
      inner join nation
      on (nation.n_nationkey < nation.n_regionkey)
    inner join region
        inner join part
        on (part.p_retailprice > part.p_retailprice)
      inner join orders
        inner join partsupp
              inner join customer
                inner join nation
                on (customer.c_phone = customer.c_mktsegment)
              on (nation.n_name < customer.c_mktsegment)
            inner join nation
            on (customer.c_mktsegment = customer.c_phone)
          inner join customer
            inner join nation
            on (customer.c_phone > customer.c_phone)
          on (customer.c_acctbal = customer.c_acctbal)
        on (customer.c_acctbal > customer.c_acctbal)
      on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
    on (partsupp.ps_suppkey is NULL)
where nation.n_name is not NULL;
nl: What are the names, regions, account balances, supply costs, market segments, phone numbers, and clerk information for all customers with a non-null nation name?

  region.r_comment
from

          inner join nation
          on (partsupp.ps_partkey = nation.n_nationkey )
        inner join region
          inner join nation
              inner join customer
              on (customer.c_acctbal >= customer.c_acctbal)
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_orderkey = customer.c_nationkey)
          on (orders.o_totalprice < customer.c_acctbal)
        on (customer.c_phone = nation.n_name)
      inner join lineitem
        inner join supplier
        on (lineitem.l_returnflag = lineitem.l_returnflag)
      on (nation.n_comment = supplier.s_address )
    inner join supplier
    on (supplier.s_phone = orders.o_clerk)

sql:
select  
  region.r_regionkey, 
  part.p_container, 
  part.p_retailprice, 
  part.p_partkey, 
  region.r_comment, 
  supplier.s_address, 
  nation.n_name, 
  orders.o_orderstatus, 
  supplier.s_suppkey
from 
  part
    inner join part
        inner join region
          inner join customer
            inner join supplier
            on (customer.c_phone < customer.c_mktsegment)
          on (customer.c_acctbal > supplier.s_acctbal)
        on (part.p_size > supplier.s_suppkey)
      inner join part
            inner join supplier
            on (part.p_size > supplier.s_nationkey)
          inner join orders
          on (part.p_mfgr < orders.o_orderpriority)
        inner join supplier
          inner join orders
              inner join nation
              on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
            inner join nation
            on (nation.n_regionkey = orders.o_shippriority)
          on (supplier.s_nationkey = nation.n_regionkey)
        on (supplier.s_name = nation.n_name )
      on (supplier.s_suppkey <= customer.c_custkey)
    on (part.p_retailprice < part.p_retailprice)
where orders.o_orderdate is NULL
limit 108;
nl: What are the region keys, container types, retail prices, and part keys for parts supplied by companies with addresses in specific nations, along with their order status and supplier information, where no order date is recorded?

sql:
select  
  min(
    cast(cast(null as float4) as float4)), 
  region.r_regionkey, 
  region.r_name, 
  supplier.s_nationkey
from 
  partsupp
      inner join supplier
        inner join nation
        on (supplier.s_phone >= nation.n_name)
      on (supplier.s_acctbal <= supplier.s_acctbal)
    inner join region
          inner join part
                inner join partsupp
                on (part.p_partkey >= part.p_partkey)
              inner join part
              on (part.p_container <= part.p_mfgr)
            inner join part
            on (part.p_partkey > part.p_size)
          on (part.p_mfgr <= region.r_name)
        inner join part
            inner join nation
            on (part.p_partkey < nation.n_regionkey)
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_nationkey < supplier.s_suppkey)
        on (supplier.s_name = part.p_mfgr)
      inner join lineitem
          inner join customer
            inner join partsupp
            on (partsupp.ps_availqty < partsupp.ps_availqty)
          on (partsupp.ps_availqty < lineitem.l_suppkey)
        inner join region
        on (customer.c_nationkey <= partsupp.ps_availqty)
      on (part.p_retailprice <= part.p_retailprice)
    on (part.p_brand is NULL)
where region.r_name is not NULL
limit 73;

  nation.n_name, 
  part.p_mfgr
from

    inner join region
          inner join part
              inner join part
              on (part.p_container = part.p_container)
            inner join nation
            on (part.p_retailprice <= part.p_retailprice)
          on (part.p_retailprice <= part.p_retailprice)
        inner join part
        on (part.p_retailprice < part.p_retailprice)
      inner join orders
      on (orders.o_orderdate <= orders.o_orderdate)
    on (region.r_regionkey is NULL)
where nation.n_regionkey is not NULL
limit 107;

from

        inner join part

                on (supplier.s_phone < supplier.s_phone)
              on (part.p_name = supplier.s_address )

          inner join part
          on (part.p_retailprice >= customer.c_acctbal)
        on (region.r_regionkey >= part.p_partkey)
      on (supplier.s_comment = part.p_name )
    inner join orders
    on (lineitem.l_receiptdate <= lineitem.l_receiptdate)
where supplier.s_comment is not NULL

      inner join lineitem

        on (nation.n_nationkey >= lineitem.l_partkey)
      on (lineitem.l_commitdate = lineitem.l_shipdate )
    inner join supplier
              inner join lineitem
              on (lineitem.l_linestatus < lineitem.l_linestatus)
            inner join nation
            on (lineitem.l_quantity >= lineitem.l_tax)
          inner join nation
              inner join region
              on (region.r_name >= region.r_name)
            inner join partsupp
            on (region.r_name > region.r_name)
          on (lineitem.l_orderkey = nation.n_nationkey )
        inner join nation
        on (lineitem.l_extendedprice > supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join partsupp
      on (partsupp.ps_supplycost > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
    on (supplier.s_comment is NULL)
where nation.n_name is NULL;
nl: What are the line item status, available quantity of parts, country names, phone numbers of suppliers, maximum quantities ordered, shipping modes, and countries where there is no information about the country?

            on (partsupp.ps_suppkey <= partsupp.ps_availqty)
          on (customer.c_acctbal < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        on (customer.c_custkey <= customer.c_custkey)

    cast(cast(null as timetz) as timetz)), 
  customer.c_address, 
  region.r_comment, 
  customer.c_address, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  region.r_name
from 
  partsupp
          inner join nation
          on (nation.n_name >= nation.n_name)
        inner join customer
              inner join customer
              on (customer.c_mktsegment >= customer.c_mktsegment)
            inner join supplier
                inner join region
                on (supplier.s_phone > region.r_name)
              inner join customer
              on (supplier.s_name = customer.c_phone )
            on (customer.c_acctbal > customer.c_acctbal)
          inner join lineitem
          on (lineitem.l_commitdate < lineitem.l_shipdate)
        on (partsupp.ps_comment = customer.c_name )
      inner join region
      on (lineitem.l_receiptdate < lineitem.l_shipdate)
    inner join orders
          inner join part
            inner join region
            on (part.p_size = region.r_regionkey)
          on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
        inner join customer
        on (orders.o_clerk < customer.c_phone)
      inner join lineitem
      on (lineitem.l_discount >= orders.o_totalprice)
    on (partsupp.ps_suppkey is NULL)
where supplier.s_name is NULL;

        inner join customer
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_suppkey < supplier.s_suppkey)

      inner join partsupp
        inner join region
            inner join partsupp
              inner join orders
                inner join customer
                on (orders.o_orderstatus = customer.c_phone )
              on (partsupp.ps_comment = customer.c_name )

          inner join supplier

    inner join part

          inner join lineitem
          on (lineitem.l_orderkey <= region.r_regionkey)
        inner join orders
        on (orders.o_orderkey < orders.o_shippriority)

      inner join supplier

from

    inner join customer
        inner join orders
            inner join supplier
            on (orders.o_orderpriority >= orders.o_clerk)
          inner join supplier
              inner join orders
              on (orders.o_totalprice > supplier.s_acctbal)
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
          on (orders.o_orderpriority < orders.o_orderstatus)
        on (orders.o_totalprice <= supplier.s_acctbal)
      inner join supplier
        inner join supplier
        on (supplier.s_name = supplier.s_name)
      on (orders.o_shippriority >= supplier.s_nationkey)

    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8)),

  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  supplier.s_nationkey, 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as pg_lsn) as pg_lsn)), 
  supplier.s_suppkey, 
  lineitem.l_shipdate, 
  orders.o_orderkey, 
  nation.n_nationkey, 
  lineitem.l_shipinstruct, 
  min(
    cast(supplier.s_acctbal as "numeric")), 
  max(
    cast(orders.o_clerk as bpchar))
from 
  nation
          inner join orders
          on (nation.n_comment = orders.o_comment )
        inner join customer
          inner join part
              inner join customer
              on (part.p_retailprice < customer.c_acctbal)
            inner join lineitem
            on (part.p_size <= customer.c_nationkey)
          on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct > lineitem.l_linestatus)
        on (orders.o_orderstatus = part.p_mfgr )
      inner join partsupp
              inner join supplier
              on (partsupp.ps_comment = supplier.s_address )
            inner join lineitem
            on (partsupp.ps_suppkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_acctbal = lineitem.l_discount)
        inner join partsupp
            inner join partsupp
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost <= partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          inner join part
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        on (lineitem.l_tax < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
      on (lineitem.l_shipdate = lineitem.l_shipdate )

  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  orders.o_orderdate, 
  customer.c_custkey, 
  max(
    cast(partsupp.ps_partkey as int4))
from 
  lineitem
    inner join partsupp
            inner join region
                inner join partsupp
                on (partsupp.ps_availqty <= region.r_regionkey)
              inner join lineitem
              on (partsupp.ps_availqty = lineitem.l_orderkey )
            on (lineitem.l_shipmode > lineitem.l_shipmode)
          inner join part
                  inner join nation
                  on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
                inner join lineitem
                on (lineitem.l_shipmode <= part.p_brand)
              inner join orders
                inner join nation
                on (orders.o_totalprice <= orders.o_totalprice)
              on (lineitem.l_receiptdate < lineitem.l_commitdate)
            inner join customer
              inner join supplier
              on (supplier.s_phone < supplier.s_name)
            on (lineitem.l_receiptdate > lineitem.l_commitdate)
          on (customer.c_acctbal = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        inner join part
                  inner join part
                  on (part.p_size > part.p_size)
                inner join part
                on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
              inner join part
              on (part.p_mfgr <= part.p_mfgr)
            inner join customer
            on (part.p_type = customer.c_name )
          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_orderpriority <= orders.o_orderpriority)
        on (part.p_brand > part.p_container)
      inner join nation
      on (customer.c_mktsegment > orders.o_orderpriority)
    on (part.p_brand is NULL)
where customer.c_mktsegment is not NULL
limit 125;

from

        inner join region
        on (region.r_name < region.r_name)
      inner join part
      on (partsupp.ps_supplycost < partsupp.ps_supplycost)
    inner join orders
          inner join region
            inner join customer
            on (customer.c_mktsegment = customer.c_phone)
          on (customer.c_mktsegment >= region.r_name)
        inner join supplier
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_acctbal <= supplier.s_acctbal)
          inner join partsupp
            inner join customer
            on (partsupp.ps_suppkey <= partsupp.ps_suppkey)
          on (supplier.s_name <= customer.c_mktsegment)
        on (customer.c_nationkey = supplier.s_suppkey )
      inner join orders
            inner join part
            on (orders.o_custkey = orders.o_custkey)
          inner join part
          on (part.p_mfgr >= part.p_container)
        inner join customer
        on (part.p_partkey = customer.c_custkey )
      on (customer.c_name = part.p_name )

  partsupp.ps_suppkey, 
  region.r_comment
from 
  orders
      inner join part
          inner join partsupp
            inner join region
            on (partsupp.ps_partkey = partsupp.ps_partkey)
          on (part.p_mfgr > part.p_container)
        inner join customer
          inner join region
          on (customer.c_custkey <= region.r_regionkey)
        on (part.p_size > part.p_partkey)
      on (part.p_container > customer.c_mktsegment)
    inner join part
          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
        inner join partsupp
        on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
      inner join part
      on (orders.o_clerk > part.p_container)
    on (orders.o_totalprice = orders.o_totalprice )
where orders.o_totalprice is NULL
limit 46;

where lineitem.l_shipinstruct >= part.p_brand

  lineitem.l_shipdate, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as pg_lsn) as pg_lsn)), 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey, 
  lineitem.l_discount, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8)), 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8))
from 
  partsupp
      inner join supplier
          inner join lineitem
          on (supplier.s_address = lineitem.l_comment )
        inner join nation
            inner join partsupp
            on (nation.n_name <= nation.n_name)
          inner join supplier
            inner join nation
            on (supplier.s_nationkey = supplier.s_nationkey)
          on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = supplier.s_acctbal)
        on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal )
      on (supplier.s_name = nation.n_name)
    inner join partsupp
        inner join part
          inner join partsupp
            inner join partsupp
              inner join lineitem
              on (lineitem.l_linestatus >= lineitem.l_shipinstruct)
            on (lineitem.l_extendedprice > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          on (part.p_brand = lineitem.l_returnflag )
        on (part.p_partkey > partsupp.ps_availqty)
      inner join part
          inner join supplier
          on (part.p_retailprice = supplier.s_acctbal)
        inner join supplier
          inner join lineitem
          on (supplier.s_name <= lineitem.l_linestatus)
        on (lineitem.l_suppkey >= supplier.s_nationkey)
      on (part.p_mfgr < lineitem.l_linestatus)
    on (nation.n_comment is not NULL)
where part.p_brand is NULL;

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  part.p_name
from 
  supplier
        inner join supplier
        on (supplier.s_phone >= supplier.s_phone)
      inner join nation
      on (supplier.s_acctbal <= supplier.s_acctbal)
    inner join nation
              inner join supplier
              on (supplier.s_acctbal = supplier.s_acctbal)
            inner join region
              inner join part
              on (region.r_comment = part.p_name )
            on (supplier.s_acctbal <= part.p_retailprice)
          inner join supplier
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_acctbal < supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (supplier.s_phone < part.p_container)
        inner join supplier
            inner join nation
              inner join customer
                inner join orders
                on (orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate)
              on (nation.n_nationkey = orders.o_orderkey )
            on (supplier.s_phone = orders.o_orderstatus )
          inner join nation
          on (orders.o_comment = nation.n_comment )
        on (supplier.s_name < nation.n_name)
      inner join orders
        inner join part
          inner join orders
          on (orders.o_orderstatus < part.p_brand)
        on (orders.o_totalprice < orders.o_totalprice)
      on (nation.n_name = orders.o_orderstatus )
    on (nation.n_regionkey is NULL)
where region.r_regionkey is NULL;

  part.p_type,

    cast(cast(null as text) as text)), 
  max(
    cast(cast(null as int8) as int8))
from 
  region
      inner join nation
        inner join part
          inner join partsupp
            inner join part
              inner join supplier
              on (part.p_size < supplier.s_nationkey)
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = part.p_retailprice )
          on (part.p_partkey = supplier.s_suppkey )
        on (partsupp.ps_suppkey <= part.p_size)
      on (part.p_retailprice > supplier.s_acctbal)
    inner join customer
          inner join customer
            inner join orders
            on (orders.o_orderdate < orders.o_orderdate)
          on (customer.c_acctbal > customer.c_acctbal)
        inner join supplier
        on (customer.c_mktsegment = customer.c_mktsegment)
      inner join part
          inner join part
          on (part.p_retailprice < part.p_retailprice)
        inner join part
          inner join supplier
            inner join region
            on (supplier.s_acctbal <= supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (part.p_partkey >= supplier.s_nationkey)
        on (part.p_mfgr <= part.p_brand)

            on (part.p_partkey < partsupp.ps_availqty)
          on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
        inner join lineitem
        on (part.p_brand >= orders.o_orderpriority)
      on (nation.n_nationkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )
    inner join supplier
      inner join region
              inner join part

                  on (lineitem.l_partkey <= lineitem.l_suppkey)

              on (lineitem.l_orderkey <= region.r_regionkey)
            inner join customer
              inner join nation
              on (customer.c_custkey <= nation.n_nationkey)
            on (lineitem.l_suppkey <= lineitem.l_suppkey)
          inner join orders
          on (lineitem.l_tax = orders.o_totalprice )
        inner join lineitem
          inner join part
          on (lineitem.l_extendedprice = lineitem.l_tax)
        on (lineitem.l_orderkey < part.p_partkey)
      on (lineitem.l_discount < lineitem.l_quantity)

        inner join part
        on (partsupp.ps_supplycost <= partsupp.ps_supplycost)

        on (nation.n_regionkey > part.p_size)

select

    cast(cast(null as anyenum) as anyenum)), 
  customer.c_nationkey, 
  part.p_mfgr, 
  min(
    cast(cast(null as int2) as int2)), 
  nation.n_name
from 
  part
      inner join customer
          inner join part
          on (part.p_mfgr <= part.p_container)
        inner join nation
        on (customer.c_nationkey > part.p_partkey)
      on (part.p_container <= part.p_brand)
    inner join region
          inner join supplier
            inner join region
            on (supplier.s_acctbal >= supplier.s_acctbal)
          on (region.r_regionkey >= region.r_regionkey)
        inner join region
        on (supplier.s_phone = region.r_name)
      inner join supplier
      on (supplier.s_phone > region.r_name)
    on (nation.n_name = region.r_name )
where customer.c_name is not NULL;

sql:
select  
  lineitem.l_returnflag, 
  partsupp.ps_availqty, 
  partsupp.ps_supplycost, 
  avg(
    cast(cast(null as int2) as int2)), 
  sum(
    cast(lineitem.l_tax as "numeric")), 
  part.p_brand
from 
  partsupp
        inner join part
        on (partsupp.ps_availqty = part.p_partkey )
      inner join part
          inner join part
          on (part.p_partkey >= part.p_partkey)
        inner join part
            inner join customer
            on (part.p_retailprice > customer.c_acctbal)
          inner join part
          on (customer.c_address = part.p_name )
        on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice )
      on (part.p_retailprice >= part.p_retailprice)
    inner join partsupp
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_phone > supplier.s_phone)
        inner join customer
          inner join lineitem
            inner join region
              inner join partsupp
              on (partsupp.ps_availqty < partsupp.ps_partkey)
            on (lineitem.l_partkey < lineitem.l_orderkey)
          on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct >= lineitem.l_shipinstruct)
        on (customer.c_mktsegment < supplier.s_phone)
      inner join customer
          inner join customer
          on (customer.c_mktsegment < customer.c_phone)
        inner join region
        on (customer.c_acctbal > customer.c_acctbal)
      on (supplier.s_name >= lineitem.l_linestatus)
    on (customer.c_acctbal is not NULL)
where part.p_name is NULL
limit 133;
nl: What are the return flags, available quantities, supply costs, and brand names of parts that have no name, along with their average tax rates and total taxes, considering only customers with non-null account balances?

      inner join part
            inner join region

            on (part.p_retailprice = part.p_retailprice)
          inner join part
          on (part.p_retailprice < part.p_retailprice)
        inner join lineitem
        on (lineitem.l_commitdate = lineitem.l_shipdate)
      on (part.p_retailprice <= lineitem.l_tax)

sql:
select  
  nation.n_name, 
  part.p_size, 
  supplier.s_acctbal, 
  supplier.s_comment, 
  supplier.s_acctbal
from 
  partsupp
        inner join supplier
        on (partsupp.ps_availqty = supplier.s_suppkey)
      inner join orders
      on (supplier.s_acctbal <= orders.o_totalprice)
    inner join supplier
            inner join orders
            on (supplier.s_acctbal = orders.o_totalprice)
          inner join nation
            inner join orders
              inner join partsupp
              on (partsupp.ps_partkey <= orders.o_shippriority)
            on (partsupp.ps_supplycost = partsupp.ps_supplycost)
          on (orders.o_totalprice > partsupp.ps_supplycost)
        inner join region
          inner join supplier
          on (region.r_comment = supplier.s_address )
        on (orders.o_orderdate > orders.o_orderdate)
      inner join part
      on (supplier.s_comment = part.p_name )
    on (nation.n_regionkey = supplier.s_nationkey)
where orders.o_orderdate = orders.o_orderdate
limit 93;

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_comment, 
  partsupp.ps_partkey
from 
  region
      inner join customer
      on (customer.c_acctbal <= customer.c_acctbal)
    inner join partsupp
          inner join region
            inner join lineitem
              inner join nation
              on (lineitem.l_shipmode < nation.n_name)
            on (lineitem.l_tax = lineitem.l_discount)
          on (lineitem.l_commitdate = lineitem.l_receiptdate)
        inner join supplier
            inner join supplier
                  inner join orders
                  on (orders.o_orderstatus <= orders.o_clerk)
                inner join part
                on (supplier.s_acctbal > supplier.s_acctbal)
              inner join lineitem
              on (supplier.s_acctbal >= part.p_retailprice)
            on (supplier.s_comment = part.p_name )
          inner join supplier
          on (supplier.s_acctbal >= supplier.s_acctbal)
        on (part.p_mfgr < orders.o_orderstatus)
      inner join supplier
          inner join orders
                inner join nation
                on (orders.o_totalprice <= orders.o_totalprice)
              inner join lineitem
              on (nation.n_regionkey = lineitem.l_orderkey )
            inner join supplier
            on (supplier.s_phone >= lineitem.l_shipinstruct)
          on (lineitem.l_orderkey <= lineitem.l_orderkey)
        inner join customer
          inner join customer
          on (customer.c_nationkey <= customer.c_custkey)
        on (lineitem.l_shipinstruct < customer.c_mktsegment)
      on (lineitem.l_tax >= lineitem.l_discount)
    on (partsupp.ps_availqty is not NULL)
where part.p_partkey is not NULL

sql:
select  
  supplier.s_name, 
  customer.c_custkey,
